==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Milestone
<hw>Mile"stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
stone serving the same purpose as a milepost.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An event or accomplishment marking a significant
advance in an endeavor; a notable achievment; <as>as, putting a man in
orbit was a major <ex>milestone</ex> on the way to the
moon</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> milepost.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Milfoil</ent>⟦br⟧
